column16: Andy LaRoche out on a sacrifice fly to right fielder Jody Gerut.    Craig Monroe scores.    Adam LaRoche to 3rd.
Eric Hinske singles on a ground ball to right fielder Jody Gerut.    Freddy Sanchez scores.    Craig Monroe to 3rd.    Adam LaRoche to 2nd.
Adam LaRoche walks.    Craig Monroe to 2nd.
Craig Monroe singles on a ground ball to shortstop Chris Burke.  Freddy Sanchez advances to 3rd, on throwing error by shortstop Chris Burke.
Freddy Sanchez grounds into a force out, shortstop Chris Burke to second baseman Edgar Gonzalez.    Nyjer Morgan out at 2nd.    Freddy Sanchez to 1st.
Zach Duke flies out to center fielder Scott Hairston.
Jason Jaramillo walks.    Ramon Vazquez to 2nd.
Andy LaRoche grounds into double play, first baseman Adrian Gonzalez to shortstop Chris Burke to pitcher Eulogio De La Cruz.    Eric Hinske out at 2nd.
Edgar Renteria grounds out, pitcher Eulogio De La Cruz to first baseman Adrian Gonzalez.
James Loney grounds out, second baseman David Eckstein to first baseman Adrian Gonzalez.
Manny Ramirez grounds out, shortstop Everth Cabrera to first baseman Adrian Gonzalez.
